{"title":"雪山上飞起三只彩凤（外二首）","authors":["廖代谦"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":3,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山上飞起三只彩凤（外二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"廖代谦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三位藏族姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三位女养路工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三朵初开的雪莲花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贝玛、卓瑁和阿容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去都是女农奴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命全被那雪裹冰封。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一汪眼泪一汪血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把农奴主的鞭子浸得通红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三位藏族姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三位女养路工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今成了生活的主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山上飞起三只彩凤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了温暖有了欢乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当上了光荣的养路工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一串歌声一身汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铲尽一路的飞雪怒风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我问她们这工作可好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贝玛指一指天边的彩虹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是赞颂这幸福的路啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像彩虹升起在雨后晴空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卓瑁两手比一比公路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿容又含笑捧住前胸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是说这通往北京的金桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像幸福浪涛在心中翻涌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青海湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山围成白玉杯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛着一湖青海水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青海水啊青海水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝湛湛更比宝石翠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云湖面起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海鸥点浪飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高原奇景真叫美！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏胞赶过来牦牛队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一曲悲歌随风飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同车的战友告诉我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲歌唱的旧社会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧社会啊青海水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一湖牧民辛酸泪……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然一响鞭声脆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲歌换欢调，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏胞笑微微。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑微微啊笑微微，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这支欢歌我能领会："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢歌唱的翻身喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"封建大山连根摧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢歌唱的建设好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖滨飞奔汽车队；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢歌唱的丰收乐啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社马壮牛羊肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满湖湟鱼把网坠……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猜的对啊也不对，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱的还是青海水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今一湖青海水啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青稞美酒斟满杯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧民的欢乐酿成它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再没有苦涩辛酸泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给恩人毛主席啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人民同口醉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日月山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千古日月山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高雪茫茫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文成公主摔宝镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银镜竖在高原上。*"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树不生啊麦不长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到此谁不思故乡！？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今日月山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金路架桥梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少战士从此过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮怀激烈把歌唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声飞满柴达木，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路笑语进西藏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日月山相传是文成公主入藏时摔破思乡宝镜所化。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}